{"tid":2053474,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[香港偽人]香港演藝界搞唔搞膽係香港大搞愛支國運動?","createTime":"2020-06-06T10:04:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-06T10:08:37.000Z","uid":90577,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6dc83045be7c43bf468f04f53c46b258378c4228","tid":2053474,"uid":90577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T10:04:31.000Z","msg":"之前64大把人搵返民主歌聲獻中華呢單野來鞭屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日話今日香港演藝界幼共,依家中美兩國幾乎到大戰邊緣<br />\n唔知香港演藝界有冇人敢提議,仿效當年民主歌聲獻中華,係香港搞反美愛國運動<br />\n例如搞個愛國歌聲抗美帝<br />\n叫晒所有偽人上台唱歌支持支國大罵美帝不是<br />\n甚至叫有美國籍既偽人公開撕毀美帝passport<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知有冇偽人夠膽咁搞?如果有,又有幾多偽人夠膽響應?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50d8eeb3a714fa93fe248dc733511f38fa964dee","tid":2053474,"uid":271130,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T10:06:02.000Z","msg":"愛國行動post 支持<br />\n<br />\n山雞哥佢地咁愛國 一家要帶頭做"},{"pid":"3266a8b34d12ddb028b48a949841f9484029dc23","tid":2053474,"uid":132587,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T10:08:37.000Z","msg":"佢地有咩唔敢<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/knU5cLQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FknU5cLQ.png&h=79cca896&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}